paths: Obvious exits: north, east, south, west
description: One of the fire niches in this room is broken, and you can see some of the inner workings.  A thin copper pipe protrudes from the cracked niche and is ruptured several inches from its end.  At that break a small flame dances, leading you to believe that these pipes must tap into some natural gas deposit.
title: [Temple Wyneb, Tanthuz]
